				<li id="16784503" class="cmnt-root" data="0" data-d="1665365973000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="https://fextralife.com/avatars/59803_1647755384.jpg" alt="" /><a class="comment-username" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&u=59803" rel="nofollow"  target="_blank" style="color: #;">Kaze</a></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t578189/Dragon-Greatclaw" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">09 Oct 2022 21:39</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16784503" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">So hear me out for a second. This is the lightest weight colossal weapon, tied with the troll  hammer—meaning it uses less stamina to swing, works well powerstanced, and is longer than half the weapons in it&apos;s class. Now for the real kicker: because of how softcaps work on unique weapons this is actually a dexterity colossal baby... at least as much as a colossal can be.  Because both the physical and lightning scale with dexterity, it greatly outpaces strength investment until you have about 70 levels to throw away; at which point it finally becomes a quality weapon.  So here&apos;s my advice if you want to build around this bad boy, level your strength until you meet the base requirements then just ignore it. Then keep pumping dexterity until you reach 47. Dump the rest into endurance to powerstance and become a beefcake. There, between endure and your armor you should be nigh unkillable.  Have fun kids.</p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16784503" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16784503" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">0</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>0</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>0</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16784503"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16784503" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16784503"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
